org.apache.camel.RoutesBuilder, Aware, ApplicationContextAware
@CamelConfiguration(value="repairProcessingExtCallRoute")
public class RepairProcessingExtCallRoute
extends org.apache.camel.spring.SpringRouteBuilder

Route definition that repairs external calls hooked in the state ExternalCallStateEnum.PROCESSING. After a specified time these external calls are changed to ExternalCallStateEnum.FAILED state without increasing failed count.
